{"tid":7791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超　寸王被逐　魔迷：又唔見你趕高普","createTime":"2016-11-28T03:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T07:18:26.000Z","uid":12027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6c85532591908ea3c9ed784e3184313d89c6f6","tid":7791,"uid":12027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3MW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=29160315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】曼聯周日英超主場，同韋斯咸打成1:1平手。除咗錘仔幫90秒極部入波之外，另中一個焦點就係紅魔領隊莫連奴被逐。 <br />\n<br />\n話說28分鐘左右，球證莫斯(Jon Moss)罰保羅普巴插水，仲要畀張黃牌普巴，搞到呢位法國國腳要喺英聯盃停賽，寸王即時無名火起，覺得球證判得太嚴，仲嬲到一腳踢走個水樽。莫斯之後走埋主隊後備席，二話不說就趕走莫連奴。 <br />\n<br />\n一班魔迷賽後都好鼓譟，話球證針對寸王。莫連奴小小事就趕出場，但係利物浦嘅高普同車路士主帥干地，喺場邊有時鬧球證就叫「熱情」，就連球評都覺得過分。 <br />\n<br />\nLiam Canning(英國球評)：呢啲偏見真係好笑喇，高普同個第4球證講粗口就熱誠，莫連奴踢樽就趕出場。 <br />\n<br />\nJordan：如果高普或者干地踢樽就係「激情」，莫連奴呢就行為不檢... <br />\n<br />\nNitish Reddy：英格蘭足總同球證擺明搵寸王嚟搞，雲格、哥迪奧拿或者高普做同一樣嘢，最多咪係警告下 <br />\n<br />\nALex：呢啲咪干地/高普正常反應，但係當莫連奴咁做呢，足總9成9會罰佢唔畀入球場，仲要「叉廚」佢45,000鎊 <br />\n<br />\nRoberto：食X啦足總！"},{"pid":"d125837a0e63b0348da6707b6e13d1c484ec6690","tid":7791,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"daddy想拉埋高daddy落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7523cd5f1885af41cbe947c5bccd6c26420eb029","tid":7791,"uid":2797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a7380232bf27e592b9c1ecd06762b027992dda","tid":7791,"uid":28394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"個格衰無計"},{"pid":"9445bd7c104d0dd8c047029fe68d883166b40933","tid":7791,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>daddy想拉埋高daddy落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要拉埋我干爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627899a75615a123206c9af1106c814828e7db11","tid":7791,"uid":4082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"次撚次都逼害daddy😭😭😭"},{"pid":"46ddf1d392d541619f179b44ddc54427040cd2a3","tid":7791,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"我幾時有踢水樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0c9dfa5d4fc255a86dce4ed672daa18738500c","tid":7791,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"我要佢果串都冇醬"},{"pid":"7321aad0d3cebb7a1ab5c5ae3e5cfeb1c2628731","tid":7791,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">雲格</span>、哥迪奧拿或者高普做同一樣嘢，最多咪係警告下 <br />\n<br />\n係撚咩 唔記得當年上帝姿勢點黎喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5766ad6885eba0bde8e1a6384de3fed488361fc6","tid":7791,"uid":24041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"唔驚啦，有冇佢咪一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c1b615e343c11ad4db0fe14079c6bb1b1252f2","tid":7791,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺掟水樽咩事都冇<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2236d4e7494e8d8ad4b1b54aaff67dde70047bcf","tid":7791,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im